      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Fish Smoker\n|image2      = Fish Smoker On\n|image2spacing = true\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = [[Fish Shop]] for {{Price|10000}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Hardwood|10}}{{Name|Sea Jelly|1}}{{Name|River Jelly|1}}{{Name|Cave Jelly|1}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Fish Smoker''' is a type of [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]] that is used to create [[Smoked Fish|smoked fish]] using any [[fish]] and 1 [[coal]]. It doubles the sell price of a fish while retaining quality, as well as multiplying the [[energy]] and [[health]] restoration by 1.5 (if that fish restored energy or health, otherwise the value remains unchanged).<ref name=\"energy\" /> The smoker accepts [[Fish#Legendary Fish|Legendary Fish]] as well as [[Crab Pot]] specific fish, making the latter edible.<ref name=\"inedible\" />\n\nIt can be crafted after purchasing the recipe from the [[Fish Shop]] for {{Price|10000}}. It is also a possible reward as the 12th prize from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]] in the Mayor's Manor (50% chance). Players on the [[Farm Maps#Riverland|Riverland Farm]] start with one Fish Smoker.\n\n==Products==\n<section begin=\"fishsmokerproducts\"/><!--Transcluded onto Artisan Goods page-->\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Image\n! Name\n! Description\n! Ingredients\n! Processing Time\n! Sell Price\n! Energy / Health\n|-\n| [[File:Smoked Fish.png]] || [[Smoked Fish]] || A whole fish, smoked to perfection. || [[File:Fish.png|24px|link=]] Any [[Fish]] (1) {{Name|Coal|1}} || {{duration|50 mins}} || 2 × Fish Price || {{Energy|1.5 × Fish Energy}}{{Health|1.5 × Fish Health}}\n|}<section end=\"fishsmokerproducts\"/>\n\n==References==\n<references>\n    <ref name=\"energy\">See <samp>ObjectDataDefinition::CreateFlavoredSmokedFish</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n    <ref name=\"inedible\">The edibility of a crab pot fish that is normally inedible is calculated as <samp>Sell Price × 0.3</samp>. See <samp>ObjectDataDefinition::CreateFlavoredSmokedFish</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.6|Introduced.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Fischräucherer]]\n[[es:Ahumador de Peces]]\n[[fr:Fumoir à poisson]]\n[[it:Affumicatore]]\n[[ja:魚のくんせい器]]\n[[ko:생선 훈제기]]\n[[hu:Halfüstölő]]\n[[pt:Defumador de Peixes]]\n[[ru:Коптильня для рыбы]]\n[[tr:Balık Tütsüleyici]]\n[[zh:熏鱼机]]"
